# Stats Module
#
# Statistics collection and reporting for the Simple compiler.
# Tracks compilation metrics, performance data, and usage statistics.
#
# Public API:
#   - use app.stats.{collect_stats, report_stats}
#   - use app.stats.{CompilationStats, PerformanceMetrics}

# All submodules are automatically available.

